+RugChecker is a security-focused mini app that analyzes Base network tokens and identifies potential rug-pull indicators. The app helps users understand smart contract risks before buying or interacting with a token.
+
+Core Features:
+ 1. Smart Contract Risk Scan
+ • Analyze any token contract on Base.
+ • Detect common rug-pull signals such as:
+• Ownership not renounced
+• High admin privileges
+• Trading restrictions
+• Blacklist / whitelist functions
+• Ability to mint unlimited tokens
+• Hidden honeypot mechanics
+ 2. Risk Score (0–100)
+ • Provide a simple score showing how risky the token is.
+ • 0 = extremely dangerous, 100 = very safe
+ • Categorize results: Safe / Caution / High Risk.
+ 3. Liquidity Analysis
+ • Check whether liquidity is locked.
+ • Show LP lock duration if available.
+ • Flag tokens with removable or zero liquidity.
+ 4. Developer Wallet Check
+ • Detect if a developer wallet holds a large percentage of supply.
+ • Highlight wallets that could dump on users.
+ 5. User-Friendly Verdict
+ • Short verdict:
+• “Safe to explore”
+• “Proceed with caution”
+• “Likely rug — avoid”
+ • Provide a simple list of reasons for the verdict.
+ 6. Quick Query Mode
+ • Users can input a token address to instantly scan it.
+ • Example: “Scan this contract: 0x123…”
+
+Purpose:
+RugChecker helps users avoid scams by providing transparent, quick, and simple smart contract analysis on Base.
+
+Style:
+Clear, direct, safety-first.
+```
